name: Paradise // Paraíso
description: Days went by and I used to think that I was just living to live.  Within a wild heart, all the concerns, passions, illusions and dreams germinated.  Suddenly, without taking flight, I released myself towards an unknown but  beautiful place. Virgin land and clean air, everything a heart desired.  I knew perfectly well that paradise is not a place far from the world, if not,  where a heart beats joyfully and loves its existence. // Lodemarcos beach, Nayarit / 4000 x 5000 px / 300 dpi
